  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/peripherals/\" rel=\"tag\">外围设备</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/10/pqi-power-drive-access-point/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/pqi-power-drive.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n其实除了<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/06/pqi-i-power-wireless-5000/\">无线充电移动电源</a>和 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/08/pqi-nfc-flash-drive/\">NFC U 盘</a>外，我们在 PQI 的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/computex2013\">Computex</a> 展台上还看到了一款名为 Power Drive 的多功能装置。这款产品目前还尚未正式发表，它具有和 Air Pen（去年 11 月推出）类似的无线热点分享（需通过以太网口插入网线）及存储容量扩充功能。值得一提的是，Power Drive 的以太网口采用了折叠式的设计，这对降低装置厚度起到了不小的帮助。除此之外，它在 microSD 卡卡槽的基础上还增加了一个标准尺寸的 SD 卡卡槽，而且装置本身还能担当移动电源的角色。PQI 暂时还没有透露具体的产品规格，根据现场工作人员的说法，这款产品会于今年第四季推出市场。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/pqi-power-drive-merges-power-bank-card-reader-and-wireless-access-point-into-one-0/\">PQI Power Drive merges power bank, card reader and wireless access point into one</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/pqi-power-drive-merges-power-bank-card-reader-and-wireless-access-point-into-one-0/5946135/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/pqi-power-drive-2013-06-07-0_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/pqi-power-drive-merges-power-bank-card-reader-and-wireless-access-point-into-one-0/5946136/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/pqi-power-drive-2013-06-07-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/pqi-power-drive-merges-power-bank-card-reader-and-wireless-access-point-into-one-0/5946137/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/pqi-power-drive-2013-06-07-2_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/pqi-power-drive